    <sec id="sec23">
      <title>Statistical methods</title>
      <p>The bootstrap test [<xref rid="ref50" ref-type="bibr">50</xref>] is typically used to assess the significance of differences between data quantified with the ROC curves. The statistical methods in this study were implemented by the iLearnPlus software toolkit [<xref rid="ref32" ref-type="bibr">32</xref>].</p>
